PLUS, 1000 rounds RARE FN ammo = 550 rounds SS195LF HOT ammo (11 Boxes of 50 rounds per/box) & 450 rounds RARE SS192 "Green Ammo" (9 Boxes of 50 rounds per/box). **** RARE SS192 “Green Ammo” was produced for ONLY 3 months before FN turned to the SS195LF. The SS192 "Green Ammo" is the predecessor to the current SS195LF which uses the same 27gr HP aluminum core bullet but with a lead free primer, hence the LF designation. The SS192 “green ammo” or environmentally friendly ammo was SS195LF ammo before they changed the name and box. The manufacture (FN Herstal) relates the labeling as a way to visibly mark the packaging so that there is a lower chance for this to be mixed up with SS192 ammunition that contains lead primer.
